Function Reference/get most recent post of user « WordPress Codex
-----------

Get the most recent post of a user.

Walks through each of a user's blogs to find the post with the most
recent post\_date\_gmt.

Usage
-----

` <?php get_most_recent_post_of_user( $user_id ); ?> `

Parameters
----------

 `$user_id` 
:   ([*int*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#Int "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*required*)
    Default: *None*

Return Values
-------------

 `` `(array)`{style="color:gray"} 
:   

Contains the blog\_id, post\_id, post\_date\_gmt, and post\_gmt\_ts

Source File
-----------

`get_most_recent_post_of_user()` is located in
`wp-includes/ms-functions.php`

